casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Gerald Rabbani KARIEM, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 159452
COA: 347327 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 29, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the March 14, 2019 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
